{"tid":1124450,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過意大利北部嘅Dolomiti?","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:41:10.000Z","uid":22920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04a50a6cd7c3dfb32feb654947cba4b0bcf49027","tid":1124450,"uid":22920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:51:16.000Z","msg":"話說七月尾會去Dolomiti個到玩5日4夜<br />\n由威尼斯入 先去Cortina d'Ampezzo住兩晚<br />\n行下三峰、Lago di Braies、Misurina湖等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再去Bressanone個邊住兩晚<br />\n去埋Funes,Val Gardena hea<br />\n雖然哩到自駕遊好方便<br />\n但由於冇人識揸車，所以只可以搭巴士 <br />\n見網上資料唔多<br />\n想問下非自駕係咪好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或尾班車收好早？<br />\n想睇埋日落先落山會唔會太遲？<br />\n<br />\n Btw Bressanone個兩晚仲未book住宿<br />\n想問下其實哩到係咪都好方便，因為係山區入面比較大嘅鎮 諗住由哩到返米蘭<br />\n我見大家都推Ortisei，Funes or Val Gardena 個到住<br />\n但因為非自駕怕出入唔方便<br />\n有冇人去過比下啲意見？<br />\n<br />\n暫時想行嘅地方都係哩啲，仲有咩值得推介歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來自google<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fv6sPcW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffv6sPcW.png&h=59e0bde0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmMgHxX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmMgHxX.png&h=816aaf9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taCr4Mh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaCr4Mh.png&h=a4fd706d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc3d4870710108aed64e6e9c0dffb4c26b7211ac","tid":1124450,"uid":8138,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"有呀 doraemon呀嘛"},{"pid":"415efd3248d17a903350bf7f06cf85752780df0d","tid":1124450,"uid":22920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc3d4870710108aed64e6e9c0dffb4c26b7211ac","tid":1124450,"uid":8138,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"有