518faae4efcbecc74be5229381afd95","tid":1124450,"uid":22920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"983dad2dd0b691b299ca7568a87b81e65210b1ed","tid":1124450,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"btw 我都係住Brixton (唔記得點串)<br />\n起碼夜晚有個town好多野食<br />\n上次撞正有live band好好氣氛<br />\n如果上山住， 冇車唔方便<br />\n想食野又冇， 如果住得唔近巴士站<br />\n預咗要拖d行李上山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:30:56.000Z","msg":"咪即係bressanone brixen囉？！<br />\n食野同行李哩啲都唔驚<br />\n因為諗住自己煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋我地backpack<br />\n主要係怕太早尾班車搞到冇得留係啲景點耐啲 <br />\n<br />\n不過最後book咗離bressanone車程10分鐘（行路一個鐘）嘅Albes鎮仔<br />\n因為間屋意外地極平 旺季成間屋兩晚先$1110<br />\n仲要包埋brixen巴士卡<br />\n房屋主話巴士站係正屋出面有車搭 <br />\n係唔知啲時間點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係平到以為係啲呃人呃airbnb<br />\n如果唔係超讚房東都唔會book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw brixen有咩景點或餐廳推介 我見個到幾大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441a327dadb5bec11d892bca4139adea4463f9b0","tid":1124450,"uid":22920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1467622d43914ce525e694baecacbfab183921","tid":1124450,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"靚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我book酒店有張交通卡送<br />\n冇記錯south tyrol入面巴士train都用得<br />\n上plose都唔洗錢<br />\n又唔會好唔方便 有d半粒鐘一班， funes一粒鐘一班，極準時<br />\n你走上山都唔預留得幾個字架啦<br />\n冇問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"真係好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前去過Grindelwald覺得阿爾卑斯山區好正<br />\n好想再去<br />\n然後偶然發現意大利都有<br />\n仲要少好多人 我諗應該仲世外桃源過Grindelwald<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋本身好鍾意影相行山<br />\nDolomiti勁多打卡景點