165187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c46fec8632184e181d10c05ffd4de9a2dd02a61","tid":1124450,"uid":18349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b5fc8b68145379e5782f31c15d9b071073b2e2d","tid":1124450,"uid":165187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7675df2794aa341c6a846a2c77be5d607d32c4b4","tid":1124450,"uid":18349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"并底之蛙淨係識瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> alps region大把地方都係靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"Alps 幾個國家都唔錯架，瑞士係情有獨鍾，你吹啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"我唔覺瑞士贏十條街， 你吹呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"咁你話邊度先可以贏Dolomiti 十條街喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64271aca460c8f47ebd1f2fc169f6f875de23933","tid":1124450,"uid":22920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"去完報告返<br />\n作為旅程最後一站<br />\n哩到真係多災多難<br />\n不過真係幾靚<br />\n<br />\n行行下三峰落大雨落埋冰雹 <br />\n仲有好多泥路勁跣 仲要行雷閃電<br />\n凍到仆街 嘴唇發紫<br />\n屌仲好似有幻覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望啲景自己對眼識zoom近遠<br />\n行到冇盡頭 無時無刻都覺得下一秒唔係look落山就俾雷電死<br />\n不過係自己on9唔睇天氣又準備不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但行完三峰一圈真係幾滿足<br />\n我見啲人話行三峰好易行<br />\n但佢講易嘅程度應該係上去個條路 <br />\n啲人通常原路折返<br />\n如果圍繞咁行落個段<br />\n落雨行真係好危險下 太斜 好多上斜落斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋要小心有高山反應<br />\n<br />\n之後由Cortina 去 Bressanone 又係波折重重<br />\n個時我網上搵唔到路線所以都係去到車站中心攞路線睇<br />\n我住個到要搭四程車<br />\n但中間個程火車個日星期日唔知點解員工話冇火車 <br />\n話要再等一個鍾會有巴士接駁<br />\n等左一個鍾又話冇巴士有返火車<br />\n要再等一個鍾火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到捱左幾個鍾濕凍又要走黎走去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後去到airbnb又出唔返Bressanone<br />\n唔知點解冇車出<br />\n搞到冇左全日兼冇野食 好彩預先買左罐頭頂肚<br />\n<br />\n不過總括而言<br />\n我會再黎，下次一定玩耐啲Bressanone 個邊<br />\n因為大城市啲 同埋啲野真係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意大利物價 瑞士嘅風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnTNTB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnTNTB3.jpg&h=c44068b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vXrpJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vXrpJL.jpg&h=bb874f56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNg4boM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNg4boM.jpg&h=3c7d15c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0p2u6Xf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0p2u6Xf.png&h=f4856af1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1AHHvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1AHHvB.jpg&h=6fb6da81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWOFuaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWOFuaD.jpg&h=a0e31e18&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}